# Booking — Cron Reminders Trigger
# M11-S04: GCP Cloud Scheduler calls this endpoint every 30 minutes.
# Handler checks which tenants have local time 06:00–06:29 and emits reminder events.
# In production, this is called by GCP Cloud Scheduler (network-protected).
# M115-S03 adds CronAuthGuard (OIDC token).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### POST /cron/reminders — trigger reminder jobs
POST {{baseUrl}}/cron/reminders

###
